{"id": 3008, "genre": 1001, "title": "什么时候你会对自己的年龄特别敏感？", "description": "我们想试着了解，“年龄”这个概念是如何通过种种不起眼的细节影响我们的生活的。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA Images）", "record_count": 2011, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190919190921XnpL14sdFr2vl0gu.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-09-21T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 347137, "content": "需要自己考虑各种各样的事情的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1647074}, {"id": 347393, "content": "开始不喜欢喝可乐，喜欢喝茶的时候～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664189}, {"id": 347138, "content": "体检的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1533703}, {"id": 347139, "content": "今年十七，他们还是叫我小朋友，但我没有发现他们有什么东西能比的过我。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1348455}, {"id": 347396, "content": "总觉得结婚是一个必须但遥远的事情，但开始变得不遥远", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664210}, {"id": 347141, "content": "发现自己再也不是全队最小的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1660548}, {"id": 347142, "content": "懷孕看醫生填年齡的時候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 754795}, {"id": 347654, "content": "比自己年龄更小的人出现在团队里 明星年龄越来越小 年龄再也不是优势了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664314}, {"id": 347402, "content": "当职业需要的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434374}, {"id": 347154, "content": "想买东西却没钱的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663595}, {"id": 347155, "content": "招聘条件：35周岁以下。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084163}, {"id": 347161, "content": "同学听到我的出生年份都会惊讶：啊，你居然是02的，好小啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441665}, {"id": 346907, "content": "面试的时候，被面试官随口问了一下年纪", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 346908, "content": "看到零零后都已经成为自己同事的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 373, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 347164, "content": "年龄不再是2开头", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663599}, {"id": 346909, "content": "填表格写到“年龄”这一栏的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 346910, "content": "看到“年轻人”这个词要稍微想一下的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 347168, "content": "每当有职场晋级机会时，面对着一条条“限于XX年X月出生前”，会很恐慌年龄", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663604}, {"id": 347182, "content": "知识不足的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657710}, {"id": 347184, "content": "女性备孕期", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616427}, {"id": 347187, "content": "9价HPV疫苗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1486050}, {"id": 347204, "content": "当发现比自己年龄小的足球运动员出现在转会新闻里时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318584}, {"id": 347205, "content": "被催婚催生孩子的时候，以及，被家长对他家的孩子说“叫阿姨”的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1659212}, {"id": 347463, "content": "小孩子吃的东西，要让着 虽然我自己也想吃 哎。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664450}, {"id": 347210, "content": "朋友结婚怀孕生子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416261}, {"id": 347211, "content": "看着同龄人做着这个年龄“应该做”的事的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321372}, {"id": 348237, "content": "看到自己白头发的时候……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796983}, {"id": 346961, "content": "开始在乎“中年”究竟是从几岁开始", "image": null, "praise_count": 82, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 347217, "content": "考一些证书以及工作考试的时候 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535728}, {"id": 347219, "content": "年份轴一直往上找的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1160463}, {"id": 347736, "content": "同事越来越小，火的明星越来越小", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475876}, {"id": 347483, "content": "在社交软件说话被问年龄，都是00后，被叫阿姨好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664497}, {"id": 347485, "content": "发现我92的都快30了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664499}, {"id": 347236, "content": "发现自己身体机能不如以前的时刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 68155}, {"id": 347242, "content": "上级年纪比你小", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1325295}, {"id": 347246, "content": "我现在还是办公室里最小的，所以，我还行，还能坚持…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992003}, {"id": 347247, "content": "被人喊叔叔的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1241793}, {"id": 347759, "content": "想把自己打扮的更年轻的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652293}, {"id": 347253, "content": "喜欢上一个比我小6岁的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1162799}, {"id": 349047, "content": "周围的朋友，都在陆续筹备婚礼的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1662713}, {"id": 347262, "content": "第一次被递烟的时侯，突然才发现“啊，原来已经是大人了吗”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1663561}, {"id": 348292, "content": "看到零零后都开始结婚的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113564}, {"id": 347284, "content": "去德国入境时，小哥问我多大，说错年龄而且少说了8岁的时候！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1559942}, {"id": 347030, "content": "大概是在父母提起工作的时候 偶尔夜深人静自己也会想想", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910388}, {"id": 347032, "content": "在美国买酒的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648893}, {"id": 347033, "content": "穷", "image": null, "praise_count": 210, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1226204}, {"id": 347034, "content": "每次网上填写出生年份的时候，以前都是鼠标滑轮滑一下就找到自己的，现在要滚好几圈   QAQ", "image": null, "praise_count": 160, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770829}, {"id": 347291, "content": "最近热看老电影，发现演员那时候真年轻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1570319}, {"id": 347036, "content": "房贷", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1544795}, {"id": 347037, "content": "身边的朋友一个个结婚的时候( ๑ˊ•̥▵•)੭₎₎", "image": null, "praise_count": 118, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427249}]}